ARM: dts: sun8i: Add common dtsi file for NanoPi SBCs

This patch provides a common file for NanoPi M1 and Neo SBC.

Those have common features below.
  * UART0
  * 2 LEDs
  * USB host (EHCI3, OHCI3) and PHY
  * MicroSD
  * GPIO key switch

